{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,61],"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,49]}]},{"pos":[609,641],"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717","linkify":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717","pos":[0,32]}]},{"content":"'function' : recursive on all control paths, function will cause runtime stack overflow","pos":[642,729]},{"content":"Every path through a function contains a call to the function.","pos":[736,798]},{"content":"Since there is no way to exit the function without first calling itself recursively, the function will never exit.","pos":[799,913]},{"content":"The following sample generates C4717:","pos":[920,957]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C4717\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C4717\"\nms.assetid: 5ef3c6c7-8599-4714-a973-0f5b69cdab3c\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Warning (level 1) C4717\n'function' : recursive on all control paths, function will cause runtime stack overflow  \n  \n Every path through a function contains a call to the function. Since there is no way to exit the function without first calling itself recursively, the function will never exit.  \n  \n The following sample generates C4717:  \n  \n```  \n// C4717.cpp  \n// compile with: /W1 /c  \n// C4717 expected  \nint func(int x) {  \n   if (x > 1)  \n      return func(x - 1); // recursive call  \n   else {  \n      int y = func(0) + 1; // recursive call  \n      return y;  \n   }  \n}  \n  \nint main(){  \n   func(1);  \n}  \n```"}